{"tid":1677399,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大博士畢業典禮　校長沒有與戴口罩畢業生握手","createTime":"2019-10-27T05:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T10:53:10.000Z","uid":278712,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"94ce65121f815cffd966ab64fc63a927b7c2c32b","tid":1677399,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fCheHOK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfCheHOK.jpg&h=d68af897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滕錦光沒有與戴口罩的畢業生握手，並示意她下台。（曾婧琪攝）<br />\n<br />\n理工大學舉行博士畢業典禮，期間校長滕錦光拒絕與戴著口罩的畢業生握手。<br />\n頒授博士學位期間，先後有兩名畢業生戴上口罩上台，其中一名畢業生上台前，有工作人員與她談話。工作人員早前在綵排期間，已呼籲畢業生上台接受頒授儀式時除下口罩，尊重儀式。<br />\n兩名畢業生繼續戴著口罩上台，接受校董會主席林大輝的頒授儀式。其後向滕錦光鞠躬時，滕錦光沒有與她們握手，並示意畢業生下台。滕錦光在出席畢業禮期間，有與其他沒有戴口罩的畢業生握手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488428-20191027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488428-20191027.htm&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOaof2S8NuZTczTYEA3Eyx%2FE%3D&h=cab0447a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488428-20191027.htm&h=7cbe9c4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488428-20191027.htm</a>"},{"pid":"040afb55cd791c09abd26955eea7d304dc8f96d7","tid":1677399,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b70d6bef7c1ed41a794aeb0f0059a00bb19fc6","tid":1677399,"uid":192272,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"理大柒夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8d66cb1268572d29ecd923e675b8da3c7dd838","tid":1677399,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0